title.narrative: As operações e manutenção apoiam para serviços de USAID A TI
Les fonctionnements et entretiens soutiennent pour des services informatiques d'USAID
Operations and Maintenance Support for USAID IT Services

description.narrative: L'entrepreneur fournira les installations, le personnel, les matériaux, l'équipement et la gestion/expertise technique pour répondre aux exigences d'infrastructure IT d'USAID et d'exploitations et d'entretien des systèmes (ORGANISATION SCIENTIFIQUE DU TRAVAIL).

O contratante fornecerá as facilidades, os pessoais, os materiais, o equipamento e a gestão/competência técnica para encontrar as operações de infraestrutura e de sistemas de TI de USAID & a manutenção (exigências de O&M).

The Contractor shall provide the facilities, personnel, materials, equipment and management/technical expertise to meet the USAID IT Infrastructure and Systems Operations & Maintenance (O&M) requirements.
